{"id": "1517194133066879097", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストの事件マスのやつで、シレストの導きの声無視したら静かにため息つかれてるぽいのめちゃくちゃウケてる", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T15:47:49.427000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517194890407186512", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストの言動が、好きすぎる(いつもの)\n感極まるとかわいい女だな……しか言うことなくなっちゃうな……", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T15:50:49.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517195926580494396", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストのミリアムへの台詞って、ミリアム自体が嫌いなのか、ミリアムそのものというよりミリアムの願いとかやろうとしてたこと自体を好ましく思わないのかどっちなんだろう\nどっちも？", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T15:54:57.034000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517197876315291922", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "海に別に詳しくないから海で喩えられてもよく分からないのですが(……)\nシレストの過去って普通か……普通か❓これ以外のシレスト自身が話してくれる過去の話見てても、シレストって過去のことを恨む気持ちが本当になさそうで萌", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:02:41.887000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1517197876344656003", "filename": "IMG_5863.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 459674, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458760640351965361/1517197876344656003/IMG_5863.png?ex=6a356821&is=6a3416a1&hm=0cfd4752c93ffdea95ef0240d1976a838c517d01fb565be055a89429ac6922de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517198878389047568", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "でも、過去のことを話すときに、皆が家族に会えなくなったこととか船を守れなかったことへの引っ掛かりは感じ取れるけど、\nなんかあんまり…、根本的な部分で、自分の使命とか祝福とか加護の信頼性そのものについての話はあんましないんだよな(？)", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:06:40.800000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517199939770257629", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストが死ぬときに、最期に(？)考えたことが、どうしてあの船は沈んだのか？なの本当にめちゃくちゃな気持ちになりますよ；；\nガチャ共有の文章でもこんな文章らしいじゃないですか", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:10:53.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517200991391318026", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "時代は違えど同郷でもエルトン船長は航船の聖女の話について野蛮と称して、その被害者のことを十分に苦しめられた存在だと言い切ってすらいるのに、\n当の本人がその風習についてこれといった怒りとか恨みとかをあんまり感じてないぽいどころか、アイデンティティを見出してる感じぽさすらあるの\nウ〜ン若干のすれ違い(？)、萌", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:15:04.579000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:16:01.518000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517203139999170763", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストさんには泣く資格があったのにどうして彼女は泣かないのか……みたいなこと言われてるテキストあるんだけど、これ激萌文章すぎて痺れる\n泣くことがないって言われると高潔で強い精神のあらわれのようにも思えるけど、実際は単に感情を無くしていただけなのが、好\nシレストの経歴見ててもこれで召喚できるレベルの(？)シルバーコアって死後できるんだ……て思うけど、シルバーコアの精神強度みたいな話っていまいちよく分からんすね", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:23:36.847000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:23:55.240000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517204134292492478", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "見れば見るほどシレストの霊性指数って……精神強度って……みたいな顔になるな", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T16:27:33.905000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517228331735716053", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "すみません、本当にゴリアテを、2凸させてください😣", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:03:43.025000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1517228331815145602", "filename": "IMG_5864.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1205140, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458760640351965361/1517228331815145602/IMG_5864.png?ex=6a35847f&is=6a3432ff&hm=61433d7ae6e5d30d5bd57ef074d85c100044e75f63b9feb3c86731548976df12&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517228525717946390", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "2凸してたら3コス待つ必要なくなる…よな？と思……", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:04:29.274000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517229273189056705", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "財布取ったときに抵抗起こすと行動力かさ増しできるの、この編成に真に必要なものは財布なのかもしれないと思い始めた⸺", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:07:27.485000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517229570862874886", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル性能面にあんまり不満ないけど炉がいっぱいのときに捕食するのだけやめてほしくなってきたな(⁉️)", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:08:38.456000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517232864956121198", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "会心型のゴリアテを使ったことないからそっちは分からないけど、出血型だと250%くらい出血のやつ盛れるから極限タイスみたいに力ガッツリ盛れる人いたらゴリアテが弱くてもなんか、いけるな(？)", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:21:43.829000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517233948743438509", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "出血バフって250%か？\nゴリアテの覚醒って与えたダメージの100%を出血に変換するだけだっけ", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:26:02.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517234184182300682", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "覚醒は付与するだけだった、じゃあ増加率150%か", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:26:58.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:27:52.012000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517262700395102250", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "シレストさんのこと、わたしは覚醒後も長期間航海してきた人だと思ってるから現代地理に詳しいと思ってるし、\n生前/覚醒後どちらでも夜空は長いこと見てきた人だとも思ってるから星もそこそこに詳しいって思ってるんだ\nお願いしたら船でどこかの国に連れて行ってくれたりしないかな⛵", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T20:20:17.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517278035647270932", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 19, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "これって、読書論とか取ってゴリアテ3を手札にすぐ戻せるような構成にしてたらの話だけど(わたしは1凸ゴリアテなのでゴリアテ3コスがないと出血面で身動き取れない)\n1ゲージ目撃破するより前に3コス使ってたら1ゲージ目撃破で行動力3追加でもらえたりするのかな(例の行動力増加バグは健在)", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T21:21:13.361000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-18T21:29:26.221000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1517228331735716053", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517280813534806078", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "なんでこのバグ残ってるんだろ\n道中の雑魚処理のときにタイス解放で微妙に残ったのをバグで増加した行動力で処理してて、ふつうになんか、これってかなりだめな部類だな……って思った", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T21:32:15.661000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1517282171642052718", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "何がってこれ道中ミリアム3コスで狂気加速しまくってるとこあるから\nバグで行動力増えて敵ミリ残しみたいな状態になると、狂気供給レベルがすごくなって次戦闘への準備が容易すぎる(語彙力)", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T21:37:39.459000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
